      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is there a need to \"debounce\" this method? Seems like it\u0027s possible that it could be called repeatedly in a short time frame.\n\nI\u0027m not entirely sure if this would produce incorrect results -- possibly the set of commits to be removed would be incorrect?",
